{
  "cells": [
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "# ✈️ Aviation Data Cleaning: Prepare for Analysis\n",
        "\n",
        "Questo notebook guida attraverso il processo di **Data Cleaning** e **Feature Engineering** del dataset [NTSB Aviation Accident](https://www.ntsb.gov/).\n",
        "\n",
        "### Obiettivi del Processo\n",
        "1.  **Standardizzazione**: Rendere i nomi delle colonne uniformi (`snake_case`).\n",
        "2.  **Qualità del Dato**: Gestire i valori mancanti (NaN) per evitare errori nei calcoli statistici.\n",
        "3.  **Conversione Tipi**: Assicurarsi che date e numeri siano nel formato corretto.\n",
        "4.  **Arricchimento**: Creare nuove variabili (come la classe di gravità) per facilitare l'analisi successiva.\n",
        "\n",
        "---"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "metadata": {},
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "import os\n",
        "import sys\n",
        "import pandas as pd\n",
        "import numpy as np\n",
        "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
        "import seaborn as sns\n",
        "\n",
        "%matplotlib inline\n",
        "sns.set_theme(style=\"whitegrid\")"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "## 1. Configurazione dell'Ambiente e Gestione Encoding\n",
        "Il dataset originale NTSB viene fornito in formato CSV con encoding **Latin-1** (o ISO-8859-1). \n",
        "\n",
        "> **Perché Latin-1?** A differenza dello standard moderno UTF-8, il dataset contiene caratteri speciali storici e nomi di aeromobili che causerebbero errori di decodifica se non caricati con l'encoding corretto."
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "metadata": {},
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "BASE_DIR = os.path.dirname(os.path.dirname(os.path.abspath(\"__file__\")))\n",
        "RAW_CSV = os.path.join(BASE_DIR, \"AviationData.csv\")\n",
        "OUT_DIR = os.path.join(BASE_DIR, \"data\", \"cleaned\")\n",
        "OUT_CSV = os.path.join(OUT_DIR, \"aviation_clean.csv\")\n",
        "\n",
        "print(f\"File sorgente: {RAW_CSV}\")"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "## 2. Caricamento ed Esplorazione Iniziale\n",
        "Osserviamo la struttura grezza e i valori mancanti."
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "metadata": {},
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "df_raw = pd.read_csv(RAW_CSV, encoding=\"latin-1\", low_memory=False)\n",
        "print(f\"Righe caricate: {len(df_raw)}\")\n",
        "df_raw.head()"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "### Analisi Preliminare NaN\n",
        "Visualizziamo l'impatto dei dati mancanti."
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "metadata": {},
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "plt.figure(figsize=(10, 6))\n",
        "missing_data = df_raw.isnull().sum()\n",
        "missing_data[missing_data > 0].sort_values(ascending=False).plot(kind='bar', color='salmon')\n",
        "plt.title(\"Distribuzione dei Valori Mancanti (Pre-Cleaning)\")\n",
        "plt.ylabel(\"Numero di NaN\")\n",
        "plt.show()"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "## 3. Trasformazione e Pulizia\n",
        "Standardizziamo i nomi e gestiamo i valori nulli."
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "metadata": {},
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "def rename_columns(df: pd.DataFrame) -> pd.DataFrame:\n",
        "    mapping = {\n",
        "        \"Event.Id\": \"event_id\", \"Investigation.Type\": \"investigation_type\", \"Accident.Number\": \"accident_number\",\n",
        "        \"Event.Date\": \"event_date\", \"Location\": \"location\", \"Country\": \"country\", \"Latitude\": \"latitude\",\n",
        "        \"Longitude\": \"longitude\", \"Airport.Code\": \"airport_code\", \"Airport.Name\": \"airport_name\",\n",
        "        \"Injury.Severity\": \"injury_severity\", \"Aircraft.damage\": \"aircraft_damage\", \"Aircraft.Category\": \"aircraft_category\",\n",
        "        \"Registration.Number\": \"registration_number\", \"Make\": \"make\", \"Model\": \"model\", \"Amateur.Built\": \"amateur_built\",\n",
        "        \"Number.of.Engines\": \"number_of_engines\", \"Engine.Type\": \"engine_type\", \"FAR.Description\": \"far_description\",\n",
        "        \"Schedule\": \"schedule\", \"Purpose.of.flight\": \"purpose_of_flight\", \"Air.carrier\": \"air_carrier\",\n",
        "        \"Total.Fatal.Injuries\": \"total_fatal_injuries\", \"Total.Serious.Injuries\": \"total_serious_injuries\",\n",
        "        \"Total.Minor.Injuries\": \"total_minor_injuries\", \"Total.Uninjured\": \"total_uninjured\",\n",
        "        \"Weather.Condition\": \"weather_condition\", \"Broad.phase.of.flight\": \"broad_phase_of_flight\",\n",
        "        \"Report.Status\": \"report_status\", \"Publication.Date\": \"publication_date\"\n",
        "    }\n",
        "    return df.rename(columns=mapping)\n",
        "\n",
        "df = rename_columns(df_raw)\n",
        "df[\"event_date\"] = pd.to_datetime(df[\"event_date\"], errors=\"coerce\")\n",
        "df = df.dropna(subset=[\"event_date\"])\n",
        "df[\"year\"] = df[\"event_date\"].dt.year.astype(int)\n",
        "\n",
        "def clean_data(df: pd.DataFrame) -> pd.DataFrame:\n",
        "    injury_cols = [\"total_fatal_injuries\", \"total_serious_injuries\", \"total_minor_injuries\", \"total_uninjured\"]\n",
        "    for col in injury_cols:\n",
        "        df[col] = pd.to_numeric(df[col], errors=\"coerce\").fillna(0).astype(int)\n",
        "    \n",
        "    cat_cols = [\"weather_condition\", \"broad_phase_of_flight\", \"country\", \"purpose_of_flight\", \n",
        "                \"aircraft_category\", \"engine_type\", \"aircraft_damage\"]\n",
        "    for col in cat_cols:\n",
        "        df[col] = df[col].fillna(\"Unknown\").astype(str).str.strip().str.title()\n",
        "    \n",
        "    return df\n",
        "\n",
        "df = clean_data(df)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "## 4. Feature Engineering Avanzato\n",
        "Estrazione dello stato USA via Regex e classificazione della gravità."
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "metadata": {},
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "df[\"total_injuries\"] = df[\"total_fatal_injuries\"] + df[\"total_serious_injuries\"] + df[\"total_minor_injuries\"]\n",
        "\n",
        "conditions = [df[\"total_fatal_injuries\"] > 0, df[\"total_serious_injuries\"] > 0, df[\"total_minor_injuries\"] > 0]\n",
        "choices = [\"Fatal\", \"Serious\", \"Minor\"]\n",
        "df[\"severity_class\"] = np.select(conditions, choices, default=\"None\")\n",
        "\n",
        "mask_us = df[\"country\"].str.contains(\"United States\", case=False, na=False)\n",
        "df[\"us_state\"] = \"\"\n",
        "df.loc[mask_us, \"us_state\"] = df.loc[mask_us, \"location\"].str.extract(r\",\\s*([A-Z]{2})$\", expand=False).fillna(\"\")"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "## 5. Riepilogo della Pulizia\n",
        "Confrontiamo lo stato finale dei dati rispetto all'invio originale."
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "metadata": {},
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "summary = pd.DataFrame({\n",
        "    \"Colonna\": df.columns,\n",
        "    \"Valori Nulli (Post)\": df.isnull().sum().values,\n",
        "    \"Tipo Dato\": df.dtypes.values\n",
        "})\n",
        "print(\"Esito della Pipeline Dati:\")\n",
        "display(summary.head(10))"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "## 6. Esportazione\n",
        "Salvataggio del dataset normalizzato."
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "metadata": {},
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "os.makedirs(OUT_DIR, exist_ok=True)\n",
        "df.to_csv(OUT_CSV, index=False)\n",
        "print(f\"Successo! Dataset pronto in: {OUT_CSV}\")"
      ]
    }
  ],\n",
